Package: phaze
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Phaze <support@phazechat.world>
Homepage: https://phazechat.world
Depends: libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0 (>= 2.36) | libwebkit2gtk-4.0-30 (>= 2.36)
Section: net
Priority: optional
Description: Phaze — encrypted chat, voice and video calls
 Phaze is an end-to-end encrypted messaging app with voice calls,
 video calls, spaces (group channels), and real-time presence.
 Messages are encrypted with NaCl box (libsodium) — the server
 never sees plaintext. Supports 2FA (TOTP), QR-code device linking,
 file and voice message sharing, and Stories.
